Package hac.javareact

Class Highscore

java.lang.Object
hac.javareact.Highscore
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Highscore>
public class Highscore extends Object implements Serializable, Comparable<Highscore>
Highscore class for storing the highscores in the file, its serializable so it can be written to the file and read from the file it also implements the writeObject and readObject methods so that the score and username can be written and read from the file.
